{"tid":762173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"🇮🇳8漢輪姦🐐　完事再嘲：「過了美好一晚」","createTime":"2018-07-31T05:04:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T21:34:00.000Z","uid":1749,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c36c550450b22cdea531e8959c0f36360ddcfc1b","tid":762173,"uid":1749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T05:04:41.000Z","msg":"印度警方周日（29日）表示，他們已拘捕了8名涉嫌輪姦1名農民所飼養的山羊，致牠重傷至死。該批男子翌日還親赴該名農民的家中，笑稱與山羊度過了一個愉快的晚上。<br />\n<br />\n該印度媒體報道，該8名疑犯於上周三（25日）晚上到哈里亞納邦的一處村落，輪姦了該頭懷孕50周的山羊。農民可汗（Aslup Khan）表示，他當晚聽到羊棚有聲音，遂趕往查看，發現羊棚門被打開，其中一隻母羊不翼而飛，他循聲音去搜索時，發現了8人的惡行。<br />\n<br />\n該批男子於翌日再到訪可汗的家，承認強姦了他的山羊，可汗聽擺憤怒不已。可汗表示，他的山羊受傷倒地不能行走，甚至茶飯不思，終在上周四死去。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2mZSdEm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2mZSdEm&d=IuKNOLbpE%2FhetUGzojZuLbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=2a629f88\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2mZSdEm</a>"},{"pid":"cebf12e0d83ce693e3a2f280623d1e64e61772fd","tid":762173,"uid":13592,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T05:16:10.000Z","msg":"點解可汗會嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97536c2d7973ff7f2fe6d5885d719a0dd9bff093","tid":762173,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T05:16:26.000Z","msg":"他的山羊受傷倒地不能行走，甚至茶飯不思，終在上周四死去。"},{"pid":"23a6c27ad5d7b1a4c73f6cf8b86557213e4ce203","tid":762173,"uid":12021,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T05:17:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"95df9a1c4f87c06e53eb7f87d18425c0c36dfffa","tid":762173,"uid":144773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T05:17:46.000Z","msg":"茶飯不思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a15cd16406f050d9f7132274f0a3a5f22c2a7b49","tid":762173,"uid":80481,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cebf12e0d83ce693e3a2f280623d1e64e61772fd","tid":762173,"uid":13592,"